  "description": "The hammerhead's bite. Phase Distortion and Wavefolder at maximum STRIFE — HAMMER at -0.9 tears both voices through cross-FM and ring modulation simultaneously. Aggressive mono bass, tight envelopes, grinding harmonics. Low filter cutoffs contain the violence. The resonance shelf at 0.28 keeps the growl from becoming noise. Play below C3 and feel the jaw close.",
